Package: blockr.dm
Title: Relational Data Management Blocks for blockr
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Christoph",
             family = "Sax",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "christoph@cynkra.com"))
Description: Provides blockr blocks for working with relational data using the
    dm package. Enables visual management of multi-table data structures,
    primary/foreign key relationships, filtering across related tables, and
    flattening to single tables. Particularly useful for pharmaceutical data
    like ADaM datasets where tables share subject identifiers.
